DISTRIBUTION: The present known distribution of the genus is restricted to lowland rainforests of continental South America. Six species were described (
Mann, 1923
; 
Borgmeier, 1939
; 
Loiácono, 1981
; 
Kistner and Davis, 1989
); we examined several undescribed species from South America. 
Loiácono (1981)
keyed Neotropical species.
